These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, roller
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: may, june
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is not the person driving the roller##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | roller   | bus  |
| Sport   | may | june |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, ritmeester
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: september, december
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is not the ritmeester-smoker##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | prince | ritmeester      |
| Pet    | september  | december |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, cola
There are 2 different nationalities: italian, nigerian
1. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
2. the italian is not the person drinking juice##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |
| Food    | cola  | juice    |
| Sport   | italian | nigerian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-4::.
