 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-5::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: gardening, filmmaking
City: edinburgh, liverpool
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is not the person traveling to liverpool##6
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to liverpool##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Movie-Genre   | gardening  | filmmaking |
| Sport         | liverpool | edinburgh      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-6::.
