The people have 2 different jobs:  firefighter, software-developer
1. the person driving the roller is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the airplane is not the firefighter##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Music-Genre   | airplane  | roller      |
| Nationality   | software-developer | firefighter |

