.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-7::.
2 different games are played: backgammon, canasta
There 2 different types of food: cabbage, pineapple
1. the person playing backgammon is in an odd position##4
2. the person playing backgammon is not the person eating pineapple##6

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1      |       2       |
| Job   | backgammon | canasta |
| Pet   | cabbage       | pineapple       |

 #################################

 
